name: Bombay Coffee Roasters

reviews.review_text: This place serves good coffee and snacking options. Loved the interiors the first floor. Instagram worthy decor, specially the hanging books and furniture. The place might be little crowded at times, we visited in an afternoon, not a big wait though.

It’s cozy but not quaint, it’s brightly lit (downstairs) but not cheery, the coffee is good but the cake portion sizes are too small. Asked for the hot chocolate which was famously advertised on the menu board but wasn’t available. The entrance is marred by a “now hiring” flyer pasted on the wall. Not complaining but not a memorable experience either.

Nice cosy looking cafe on the outside. It's a hostel/co-working cafe. They didn't have hot chocolate and cold coffees available on the weekend which was disappointing! Mocha was good. There are no vegetarian bakery options as all of them contain eggs. You can work from here. Very simple cafe but there's a lot of room for improvement.

description:
**Bombay Coffee Roasters: A Cozy Coffee Haven in Caranzalem**

Nestled in the vibrant neighborhood of Caranzalem, Bombay Coffee Roasters shines with a commendable rating of 4.2 stars based on 689 reviews. This charming café has quickly garnered attention for its cozy atmosphere and inviting decor, making it a favorite among locals and visitors alike. Many patrons praise its excellent coffee and snacking options, with recurring themes highlighted in customer feedback such as "hostel," "wifi," "interiors," and "book," making it a delightful stop for students, remote workers, and coffee enthusiasts.

### Ambiance & Design

Walking into Bombay Coffee Roasters, you're immediately greeted by an aesthetic that’s both modern and warm. The interior showcases a captivating design, particularly on the first floor where unique elements like hanging books and thoughtfully arranged furniture create an Instagram-worthy ambiance. The space is bright, with ample natural light streaming through, although some reviewers noted that while it feels cozy, it may not strike a quaint vibe. Customer reviews reflect a mixture of busy, lively energy—especially during peak hours—where the café can fill up quickly, though patrons have reported minimal waiting times.

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The café prides itself on its diverse menu, featuring good coffee and a selection of snacking options. Signature drinks like mocha have received positive feedback; however, some customers have expressed disappointment over the limited availability and portion sizes of certain offerings, particularly cakes and hot chocolate. Unfortunately, dietary options for vegetarians are also limited, as all bakery items contain eggs. Presentations of food and beverages complement the overall aesthetic of the café, making each dish appealing—an aspect highlighted in attractive customer-submitted photos. 

### Customer Experience & Service

In terms of service, patrons have shared mixed experiences. While many compliment the friendly nature of the staff, others noted areas where the service could be improved, such as availability of advertised items and attention to detail regarding orders. The café operates as a hostel/co-working space, catering to those looking to work in a relaxed environment; this dual purpose, while popular, can lead to a bustling atmosphere. Reservations may not be necessary, but the café fills up quickly, particularly on weekends.

### Popularity & Reviews

The buzz surrounding Bombay Coffee Roasters is palpable on social media, with photos circulating that showcase both the vibrant food offerings and the unique decor. Most patrons share a sentiment of enjoyment, appreciating the vibe and the coffee, although suggestions for improvement have been made regarding menu variety and portion sizes. While it may not be the place for a quiet afternoon if the crowds deter you, the ambiance and aesthetic charm make it a noteworthy stop. 

### Utilizing Visual Content

Visually, the café stands out, as evidenced by various customer photos. [One shot](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnuI7U46uXH-iCG4E5IPrurBTRauN_YIujCkwri_R3Psl2GT1jS9OgVJAXJfU58qVWkHCljDQZSDLVe5hQ1cROdMzrpsuWAaQz0-cj0qHFNz-k_tHL5NNRABHmeo-z8tzh_KFm0IQ=w750-h563-p) highlights the striking interiors, adorned with delightful decor, while [another image](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdl4BbKllkoEP5bFICErTjMoLK1UmSSVMHrM7LwCQ3GRWcHyk9EDov5xiuaOgpAxwO3KsKAtHUNUhpL42_hgi6MIqfu0GcZ-yM38LgTv1cYPQrLE1lVQ9WF3s-icoU4hvQsGnxFJ=w375-h281-p) captures the presentation of the coffee, reinforcing its reputation for quality brews. 

In conclusion, Bombay Coffee Roasters is more than just a coffee shop; it’s a community hub designed for enjoyment and productivity alike. With a few areas for potential growth, it offers a delightful experience for those seeking quality coffee in an inviting setting.
